@HostelManagementApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5125

### Get Weather Forecast
GET {{HostelManagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/weatherforecast
Accept: application/json

### Test Database Connection
GET {{HostelManagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/users/test-db
Accept: application/json

### Get All Users
GET {{HostelManagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/users
Accept: application/json

### Get User by ID
GET {{HostelManagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

### Create a New User
POST {{HostelManagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "city": "Mumbai",
  "state": "Maharashtra",
  "docType": "Aadhar",
  "docNumber": "1234-5678-9012"
}

### Update a User
PUT {{HostelManagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "city": "Pune",
  "state": "Maharashtra"
}

### Delete a User
DELETE {{HostelManagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

###
